spec_data.Name: texlive-repeatindex
spec_data.Description:
This Package repeats item of an index if a page or column break
occurs within a list of subitems. This helps to find out to
which main item a subitem belongs.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:43:17 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Repeat items in an index after a page or column break
